{
  "stem": "27335.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Marmoros. ?] Yeah, that's how I know so much about, because I heard it from my father.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's-- politically the war ended there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It ended when the Austro-Hungarian army was forced back to Marmoros, to Marmoros to get in and so on the area there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Count Karoly he was a count.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he was, I don't know, own about 200,000 acres of land.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so on, but he became the first so-called, so-called democratic revolutionary, and established the first-- first republic in October, 1918.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then everything, everything fell apart.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was the end of the second-- or the First World War-- at least on the part of the Austro-Hungary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I cannot remember.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only time I can remember, back to 1918, that my-- my mother's youngest-- youngest brother got wounded on the Romanian front.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Finally, in the last-- last half year, last six months of the First World War, Austro-Hungary, eh, declared war-- war on Romania.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my young-- young uncle, because he was really only about 17, 17 years old when he was drafted and sent out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he got wounded, in the [NON-ENGLISH] in Transylvania.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There, he was in a military hospital, and my mother-- my mother took me down there to-- to visit my brother.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were just outside a tent, laid out as wounded people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was so-- so bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I remember that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was in late-- late 1918.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, then he was-- he was, well, the Russian front collapsed-- you see, came-- came the revolution.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there were-- and in Russia, the-- and the war ended on the ports, and my father was with his unit, was transferred onto the-- to the Italian front.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there, they operated again.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
